Subject: Re: [T2] Vacuum Idle Retard connection - 71 DP

--- Gregory Urban <urban(-at-)yaic.com> wrote:
 
> Currently, I have a hose running from the left side
> of the intake manifold 
> to what I believe is the vacuum advance (which is
> the nipple on the outside 
> of distributer facing backwards, away from the
> distributer).<<
>  Where does the idle retard hose connect to?<<

On your 34-pict3 carb, there should be a vacuum port
on the rear of the carb body, facing toward the rear
of the bus. This is where the retard vac hose
connects.  


